item.title: Google knows just what we need
item.description:
Google knows just what we need

Meet Destinations on Google. It's designed to help you discover and plan your perfect vacation on the go by doing the heavy lifting for you. Simply search with Google on your mobile for a state, country, or continent you'd like to travel to and add the word "vacation" or "destination" to get the stuff you need at your fingertips.

item.title: Printables
item.description:
Printables

When it comes to business cards, I rely on my digital printer MOO.COM. It is super easy! MOO is an award-winning digital printer with a difference. They make Business Cards, MiniCards, Postcards, Stickers and more – and uses premium quality paper as standard (no hidden costs!) MOO was founded in 2014, from a passion for beautiful, high-quality printed products and a love of great design – for everyone.
